The paper is focused on privacy metrics, which are commonly used in the field of computer security (cs.CR) and cybersecurity (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the categorization of privacy metrics based on the type of data that needs protection, which is related to data management (cs.DB). The paper also presents a method for choosing privacy metrics, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and statistical analysis (cs.SI).
